{"tid":2510791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電視台出身的藝人如果紅了，很少會再拍電視劇，但日本就不同","createTime":"2021-04-30T11:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T12:18:03.000Z","uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"edde3b7846733d6fb11426edf57558914594d30c","tid":2510791,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:43:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ISJYCH/posts/10158069830073034\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FISJYCH%2Fposts%2F10158069830073034&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=3795bcbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ISJYCH/posts/10158069830073034</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：袁志豪<br />\n<br />\n電視台的問題，個人觀察是發生在更早之前&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n香港電視台出身的藝人如果紅了，很少會再拍電視劇，但日本就不同，那些國民級偶像經常還是會出現在日劇中，這種差異其實說明了香港長久以來的問題。"},{"pid":"522f360a0f7a89a3490074f90332e00a87e2819b","tid":2510791,"uid":379538,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:45:28.000Z","msg":"其實係香港電視台問題<br />\n人工低、待遇差、題材單一 <br />\n你睇下上咗神台嗰班港星返大班拍劇<br />\n一集幾十萬"},{"pid":"a3d891cbb7faca6b876f094801f5834277814557","tid":2510791,"uid":27416,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:49:54.000Z","msg":"係日本問題<br />\n全世界電影地位都係高於劇"},{"pid":"8dc00d9dfe92e656c5d4ec254189e22ef2e95ad1","tid":2510791,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3d891cbb7faca6b876f094801f5834277814557","tid":2510791,"uid":27416,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:49:54.000Z","msg":"係日本問題<br />\n全世界電影地位都係高於劇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"同意，日本係少數電影發展得差過電視嘅國家"},{"pid":"7b86a49c5cd01556d4b56db983d86e7c76034422","tid":2510791,"uid":80072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"因為日本電影垃圾"},{"pid":"ba2472da9a7852328190536beb7794132fa82fca","tid":2510791,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:02